          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "High purity gold layer with thicknesses between 0.1",
                "and 0.3 um evaporated onto thin aluminum foil, or",
                "self-supporting gold foils with thicknesses of",
                "0.6-0.7 um."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "LEGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " or LEPS low-energy photon spectrometer"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "EDEG",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Targets were irradiated one by",
                "one at different particle energy for 20 - 34 h with",
                "1 - 2.5 uA beam intensity in a Faraday-cup like",
                "target holder with -300 V suppression voltage.",
                "Absolute detector efficiency was determined at 10 cm",
                "wich then was converted to closer geometry 3 cm by",
                "measuring the same source at both distances several",
                "times.",
                "Spectra were recorded in every hour, than spectra were",
                "summ up to reduce the statistical uncertainty below",
                "10%. This spectrum summing was done separately for",
                "each of the studied peaks.",
                "Decay data were taken from NUDAT online data library."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The effective energy in each case is taken at",
                "the middle of the target. The energy loss is",
                "calculated with SRIM. The energy uncertainty",
                "determined by the initial beam-energy uncertainty",
                "of 0.3%. The effect of the target thickness and",
                "energy loss on beam-energy uncertainty is 0.005-0.05%",
                "and thus neglected."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The uncertainty of the cross sections",
                "are estimated in the  standard way as the square root",
                "of the quadratic summation of the independently",
                "contributing parameters."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
